content: CommunityJoin the Ozone CommunityOzone is a global, decentralized network with validators and community members from all around the world. Join the discussions on Discord and stay upto date with the latest news and announcements      Ozone Chain is the world’s first quantum-resistant blockchain that has integrated bleeding-edge quantum security technologies in its design. Develop secure, scalable, and user-friendly apps for mission-critical domains. Ozone Chain believes in Quantum secured blockchain for solving the real-world concerns faced by Quantum computers. Ozone Chain is a decentralized platform that enables developers to build scalable user-friendly dApps with low transaction fees without ever sacrificing on security.The Ozone Chain team has officially launched their Mainnet as well as the Pree-sale. They are now here with the signature campaign to share the exciting news and contribute to the project's success. Don't miss this opportunity to be a part of the Ozone Chain Signature campaign! Initially, the campaign will run for 4 weeks. As a Campaign Manager, I guarantee that I am holding a 1 week fund ($1000). The team will drop the fund in my wallet before starting every week.Rules and Requirements Participants feel free to keep discussion on in the Ozone Chain Ann thread.You must wear the appropriate Signature, Avatar to be eligible for paymentA minimum 10 constructive posts each week must be done. If you fail to meet the minimum you will not get any payment for that week.Less than 150 characters long post will not be countedThe posts are in Off-Topic, Archival, Games and Rounds, Politics & Society,  Press, Local Board, posts in any bounty and signature campaign thread, and Posts where signature does not show are not counted as eligible.If you fail to make the min posts two weeks in a row, you will be removedYou can not make posts with AI-generated text. If you do you will be marked as an abuser and blacklisted from any type of my campaigns Any type of spamming or burst posting is not allowedIf you are tagged by any DT with a Legitimate reason you are not eligible to apply for this campaignYou will be removed without any payment if you get a negative tag during enrolling in this campaignYou must only use the Ozone chain signature in your profile. You can not use other projects' signatures.Alternative accounts are not allowed. If we find you are enrolling with more than one bitcointalk account. You will be removed and taggedA min of 5 merits need to earn in the last 120 days to be eligible of applying in this campaignOzone Chain reserves the right to disqualify any users / change any rules at any timeAs a campaign manager I reserve the right to disqualify any user and change any rules at any time Particiapnts will be paid directly to their Bitcoin address.Local Board posts will not be counted as eligible.Payouts & Positions:Staff Member -   5$/post   (min 10 posts & max 20 posts)8x Hero/Legendary members -   3.5$/post   (min 10 posts & max 20 posts)8x Sr members -   2$/post   (min Friday).Posts after 23:59 UTC Saturday will be counted towards the following week.SIGNATUREFull
